files in this directory: 

cifar_classification_bigrams.py - main script to do patch-pair based classification using the "mini cifar" dataset 

patchpair_encoder.py - defines a three-way autoencoder for learning representations of patch-pairs and their spatial relations (used by cifar_classification_bigrams.py) 

train.py - helper module that defines the trainer object used by cifar_classification_bigrams.py 

dispims_color.py - helper module for displaying learned color filters 

harris.py - helper module for extracting keypoints 

logreg.py - logistic regression 

minimize.py - conjugate gradients code (originially by carl rasmussen) used by logreg.py

make_cifarmini.py - script that makes the mini cifar dataset and dumps it in the curret directory


